![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b59a8bb5-c30d-47f6-bcda-688eab465501/e271.jpg?format=original)

Quantumania is HERE, and with it comes CHAOS in the form of a time-traveling CONQUEROR named KANG! Join us as we discuss the latest entry into the MCU, and all of that is set in motion after the events of Ant Man 3! We're also talking rumors regarding Avengers: Kang Dynasty, responses for the test screening of Aquaman 2 and much much more in this jam-packed edition of the Major Issues Podcast!  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
